public void setGenericFile(GenericFile<T> file) {     this.file = file. }
@Override public GenericFileMessage<T> newInstance() {     return new GenericFileMessage<>(getCamelContext()). }

@Override @SuppressWarnings("unchecked") public void copyFrom(Message that) {     super.copyFrom(that).     if (that instanceof GenericFileMessage) {         setGenericFile(((GenericFileMessage) that).getGenericFile()).     } }

@Override public String toString() {     // only output the filename as body can be big     if (file != null) {         return file.getFileName().     }     return getClass().getName() + "@" + Integer.toHexString(hashCode()). }
